          { text: "Focus on economic forecasts only", pts: 0 },
          { text: "Use AI to simulate economic growth", pts: 3 }
        ],
        insight: "Use backcasting: define your ideal future first, then plan how to get there ‚Äî don‚Äôt let past systems define future outcomes."
      },
